Couple Joy relies on select third-party service providers to deliver, maintain, and improve our Platform. These providers assist us in areas such as data storage, communication, analytics, and security. While these services are integral to our operations, we ensure that your personal data is handled responsibly and securely in accordance with this Privacy Policy and applicable legal standards. We partner with reputable third-party providers to perform specific functions on our behalf, including but not limited to:
Data Hosting and Storage:
Your data, including any photos and videos you upload, is stored securely using services such as Google Cloud, Cloudflare, and Amazon Web Services.
Email and Communication:
Services that facilitate the sending of notifications, updates, and marketing emails.
Support and Maintenance:
Tools and platforms that help monitor and improve the functionality and performance of our Platform.
These third parties are bound by contractual obligations to protect your data and use it only as instructed by us. They are prohibited from accessing or using your information for any other purpose.
While these services have access to certain data necessary to perform their functions, we take care to minimize the information shared and ensure it is protected. For example, we do not grant these providers access to your entire photo library—only the content you specifically choose to upload to our Platform. All third-party service providers must comply with strict data protection standards.
We do not permit third-party providers to use your data for their own purposes, nor do we sell your personal information to third parties. Data sharing is limited to what is necessary to deliver our services, maintain platform functionality, and comply with legal requirements.
We are committed to transparency regarding the third-party services we use and will update this Privacy Policy if our practices change. If you have questions about a specific service provider or wish to learn more about how your data is shared, please contact us using the details in the
Contact Us
