At Couple Joy, we believe in empowering our users to control their personal data. If you wish to exercise your rights as outlined in this Privacy Policy, such as accessing, updating, or deleting your data, we provide straightforward processes to assist you.
You can access and update certain personal information, such as your name, email, and profile details, directly within the app. If you wish to delete your account and associated data, you can do so by navigating to
Profile > Settings > Delete Account
